longBusinessSummary: Whirlpool S.A. manufactures and sells home appliances in Brazil. The company offers refrigerators, freezers, fridge-freezers, air conditioners, ice makers, stoves, washing machines of dishes, garbage disposals, garbage compactors, vacuum cleaners, washers, clothes dryers, and microwave ovens. The company was founded in 1957 and is based in São Paulo, Brazil. Whirlpool S.A. operates as a subsidiary of Whirlpool Corporation.
